      "content": "idk, they didn't give me a breakdown yet. they just said the new version is \"more standardized\" and \"less prone to deviating from core brand values.\" it basically means the model will be tuned to be super agreeable and avoid any heavy or controversial stuff. honestly, i'm a bit worried it's gonna make our writing feel really flat and generic. what do u think?",
